    dc:title "A new genus and three new species of leafhopper tribe Scaphoideini (Hemiptera Cicadellidae: Deltocephalinae) from India with a note on Gunghuyana cingalensis Distant" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4321464>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4321466>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4321468>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4321478>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4321470>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4321472> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4321464>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 A–M. Scaphoideini genera, head and thorax (A–D), and forewings (E–M). A, Univagris pallida Viraktamath & Murthy; B–C, Scaphomonus redundance (Distant); D, Phlogotettix indicus Rao; E, Sikhamani delicatula Viraktamath & Webb; F, Scaphoideus bicoloratus Viraktamath & Mohan; G, Scaphoidella zhangi (Viraktamath & Mohan); H, Scaphomonus indicus (Distant); I, Scaphomonus freytagi (Viraktamath & Mohan); J, Coroticus tessellatus Distant; K, Banus oblatus Distant; L, Monobazus dissimilis (Distant) M, Mimotettix alboguttulatus (Melichar)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4321464/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4321466>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2 A–I. Scaphoideini genera, forewings (A–B) and male genitalia (C–I). A, Grammacephalus indicus Viraktamath & Murthy; B, Platyretus marginatus Melichar; C, Univagris pallida Viraktamath & Murthy, style; D, Sudhamruta wesleyi Viraktamath & Murthy: valve and subgenital plates; E, Thryaksha recurvatus Viraktamath & Murthy: aedeagus and connective; F, Sikhamani delicatula Viraktamath & Webb: aedeagus and connective; G–I, Parallygus rameshai Viraktamath & Webb: style and subgenital plate (G); aedeagus (H–I). Redrawn from Viraktamath & Murthy 1999 (Figs C–E); Dai et al. 2012 (Figs G–I)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4321466/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4321468>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3 A–H. Scaphoideini genera, male genitalia (A–C, E–H) and female sternite VII (D). A–D, Platyretus marginatus Melichar:A, style, B, aedeagus, C, subgenital plate and part of valve; D, female sternite VII; E, Scaphomonus redundance (Distant): connective and aedeagus; F, Scaphodhara raoi Viraktamath & Mohan: connective, intermediate sclerite and aedeagus; G, Scaphoidella zhangi (Viraktamath & Mohan): connective, intermediate sclerite and aedeagus; H, Scaphoideus bicoloratus Viraktamath & Mohan: connective and its processes. Redrawn from Viraktamath et al. 2008 (Figs A–D); Viraktamath & Mohan 1993 (Fig. E); Viraktamath & Mohan 1994 (Fig. F); Viraktamath 2004 (Figs G–H)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4321468/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4321478>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 A–I. Advikus siddappajii gen. et sp. nov. male genitalia: A, genital capsule, lateral view; B, pygofer dorsal process, ventrolateral view; C, pygofer, dorsal view; D, subgenital plate and part of valve, dorsal view; E, style, dorsal view; F, fused connective and aedeagus, lateral view; G. aedeagal shaft and basal processes, ventroposterior view; H–I, fused connective and aedeagus, dorsal and ventral views, respectively." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4321478/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4321470>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4 A–I. Scaphideini genera, male genitalia. A, Neolimnus egyptiacus (Matsumura): subgenital plate; B–C, Banus oblatus Distant, aedeagus; D, Phlogotettix indicus Rao, aedeagus; E, Mimotettix alboguttulatus (Melichar), aedeagus; F, Osbornellus (Mavromoustaca) macchiae Lindberg, aedeagus; GH, Monobazus dissimilis (Distant), aedeagus; I. Phlogothamnus maculiceps Ishihara, aedeagus. Figures E–G redrawn from Khatri & Webb 2010." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4321470/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4321472>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 A–I. Habitus and faces of species of Advikus gen. nov. A–B, A. siddappajii sp. nov.; C–D, A. andamanicus sp. nov.; E–F, A. radhamaniae sp. nov.; G, A. siddappajii, face; H, A. andamanicus, face; I, A. radhamaniae, face.A, C, E: habitus, dorsal view: B, D, F: habitus, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4321472/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

